example.en:
[Example 32](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#ex163-jsonld)

 ```json 
{
  "@context": "https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams",
  "summary": "Sally listened to a piece of music",
  "type": "Listen",
  "actor": {
    "type": "Person",
    "name": "Sally"
  },
  "object": "http://example.org/music.mp3"
}
```

